{"tid":2168914,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有咩可悲得過香港人教美國人投票","createTime":"2020-08-22T05:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T10:54:10.000Z","uid":61348,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2774f4d9628bd28c865f370e287e8781740fe35","tid":2168914,"uid":61348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:56:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 ，人哋成百年投票歷史<br />\n<br />\n你班賤種香港畜牲呢？特首都無得你投喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你憑咩教人投票？<br />\n<br />\n收皮喇你班垃圾香港雜種狗，學支那人一樣教外國人投票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人哋投咩關你閪事咩，人地投個奶中總統又點，乜你又得反對咩？成班傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好可悲你班無得投票既奴隸獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e6e8b384219607f50657ed2daa06e381ea7303","tid":2168914,"uid":177213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5yaPfEa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5yaPfEa.png&h=a5c38f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1m85yqR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1m85yqR.png&h=e6ba89ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dd8d9ff6260248b560080355eb2f3cad3e3e403","tid":2168914,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:57:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f12ee9e1b691591dd593810b3bb2cda477acf10e","tid":2168914,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"079ddb7d1cc507dcdde538a74aca5baa846f7fbf","tid":2168914,"uid":61348,